-- Freddie and Fannie shares open lower on capital fears
-- 
-- Thu Jul 10, 2008 10:17am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/10/us-fanniemae-stocks-idUSN1048564920080710

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Freddie Mac and Fannie Mae posted sharp losses at the market open on Thursday on persistent fears that the two providers of home financing may need a substantial injection of capital. 

 Shares of Freddie and Fannie fell as much as 16 percent on the New York Stock Exchange. (Reporting by  Walter Brandimarte ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)